                    <button>Know More</button>
                </div>
                <div class="star-two">
                    <div class="main-star">
                        <img class="main-star" src="https://www.starbucks.in/assets/images/guest-bg-star-right.png"
                            alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="banner-two">
                <div class="details">
                    <h1>
                        Ruby, our barista has a message for you
                    </h1>
                    <p>Free coffee is a tap away. Join now to start earning rewards
                    </p>
                </div>
                <img src="https://preprodtsbstorage.blob.core.windows.net/cms/uploads/Group_977_6e5853906b.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="faq">
                <h1>How to collect stars
                </h1>
                <hr>
                <p><img src="https://preprodtsbstorage.blob.core.windows.net/cms/uploads/create_account_7371e188d6.png"
                        alt="">Create an account to get access to full range of Starbucks Rewards Benefits</p>
                <p><img src="https://preprodtsbstorage.blob.core.windows.net/cms/uploads/starfor_spend_bf8f7b7350.png"
                        alt="">Earn a star on every Rs 300 spent on your registered Starbucks Card</p>
                <p><img src="https://preprodtsbstorage.blob.core.windows.net/cms/uploads/earn_stars_redeem_rewards_e0be5531df.png"
                        alt="">As you earn stars, you can redeem them for rewardsâ€”like free drinks, and more when you
                    annually spend Rs 600 or more.</p>
                <button class="learn-btn">Learn More</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
